                <h1 class="fw-bolder lh-1">Farmer's Hub</h1>
                <p class="mt-3">A one-stop-shop for farmers' agricultural needs. This hub is to maintain a link between small farmers who need information on the go and an advisory service that caters to improving agricultural production. </p>
